iManager is an multi-platform iPhone manager developped using Qt.
With iManager, you can browse your SMSs, Calendars, Notes, Contacts, Calls, Contacts Pictures, but you
can also edit them, backup them in a secure way using advanced cryptographic features.
This way it's even possible to restore your iDevice via iTunes.

Under the GNU General Public License.
For GNU/Linux, Mac OS and Windows. 

Requires iTunes to work and at least a valid iTunes backup of your iDevice.

